{"tid":1058793,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"「足球心理學」 無退路，就係出路","createTime":"2019-03-12T19:24:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-13T01:27:22.000Z","uid":123335,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d4b6838516b6e3078444222b403be4b8f32bf42f","tid":1058793,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T19:24:20.000Z","msg":"人類就係咁犯賤<br />\n往往係要冇退路嘅時候<br />\n先會爆發曬啲潛能出嚟，表現得極高水準<br />\n<br />\n<strong>冇退路<br />\n就係出路</strong><br />\n<br />\n特別係C朗拿度<br />\n承受嘅壓力越大，越係處於逆境之中<br />\n潛能就會喺呢一瞬間爆發<br />\n世界盃 C朗帶葡萄牙一度陷入逆境中苦戰西班牙一役，<br />\n盡見C朗打逆境波真係世一<br />\n果種眼神，果種心態<br />\n堪稱逆境球王<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gJvvaWN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgJvvaWN.jpg&h=f29d4936&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o08c8Jt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo08c8Jt.jpg&h=4b1f06d4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9a1efb9d11f1c3edc26ac24a41a0dba1828c7ac6","tid":1058793,"uid":135959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T19:43:17.000Z","msg":"Bill gor 要支持了"},{"pid":"dfa1904445f3ed028be236081f5758965fcd9c4d","tid":1058793,"uid":59333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T19:46:10.000Z","msg":"彪哥why 咁耐唔入黎"},{"pid":"d31792c4333a4ff9ce603d642af618dde81e14cc","tid":1058793,"uid":92500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T22:25:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"82c42229d61ed720c443b0551478d585aaa39fdf","tid":1058793,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dfa1904445f3ed028be236081f5758965fcd9c4d","tid":1058793,"uid":59333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T19:46:10.000Z","msg":"彪哥why 咁耐唔入黎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T01:16:59.000Z","msg":"呢排少賭 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95cdffe6587a39695865071155a61bf48a6f5ea4","tid"